name: PT 1. FLACO GOES TO TEZO BELL
description: LATE LAST NIGHT WHILE WATCHING STRANGER THINGS A COMMERCIAL FOR TEZO BELL CAME FLASHING ON THE TV. IT HAD BEEN ABOUT A YEAR SINCE THE LAST RESTURANT IN TOWN HAD CLOSED UP. WITH THE NEW RESTURANT NOT BEING TOO FAR FROM HOME FIGHTING THE HUNGER AND URGE FLACO HOPPED IN THE CAR AND SPRINTED TO TEZO BELL. TO BE CONTINUED.......
